title: Real Account
description:
In a world driven by fictionalized friendship, courtesy of the program named "Real Account", the table suddenly turns, and the cybernetic world turns real! How will they survive?

[b]Note:[/b] So... This manga is [i]technically[/i] a two part... the first 10 chapters are part 1 and the 11 onward is part 2. In the past it's been split up into two series(Real Account & Real Account II).
